  "body": "<img src=\"https://cdn-raw.modrinth.com/data/Q0XHpuQz/images/909631a5c391c2af33e6157c93ad10b4c129a5a0.png\">\n\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/MvH7yqg.png\">\n\n<center><h3>Dashboard adds several switchers like the game mode switcher for other things such as Weather, Time, and Difficulty.</h3></center>\n\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/MvH7yqg.png\">\n<center>To open the menu you do it the same way you would with the game mode switcher but instead of F4 you use one of the corresponding keys.</center>\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/MvH7yqg.png\">\n\n<blockquote>\n<h1>Menus</h1>\n<h3>🌈 [F5] Weather Switcher</h3>\n<h3>⌚ [F6] Time Switcher</h3>\n<h3>💀 [F7] Difficulty Switcher</h3>\n</blockquote>\n\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/MvH7yqg.png\">\n\n<blockquote>\n<h1>Credits</h1>\n<h3>💻 Developer - ThatGravyBoat</h3>\n<h3>🎨 Icon - Lucide.dev</h3>\n</blockquote>\n\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/MvH7yqg.png\">\n\n<!-- Removal of this will cause it to come back again in a more annoying way to remove -->\n<a href=\"https://bisecthosting.com/gravy\">\n  <strong>\n    <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/d4KNMMe.png\">\n  </strong>\n</a>",
